@startuml
title Study App - C4 L2 Container View

top to bottom direction

actor "Client app" as Client

package "Study App\n(single process)" as Proc {
  [HTTP · FastAPI routers] as Http
  [Application services] as App
  [Persistence · repositories] as Persist
  Http -[hidden]down- App
  App -[hidden]down- Persist
}

database "SQLite\nstudy_app.db" as Db
rectangle "Alembic\n(migrations)" as Mig

Persist -[hidden]right- Db
Mig -[hidden]down- Db

package "Observability stack\n(Docker Compose)" as Obs {
  [Grafana] as Graf
  [Prometheus] as Prom
  [Blackbox exporter] as Bbx
  Graf -[hidden]right- Prom
  Prom -[hidden]right- Bbx
}

Proc -[hidden]down- Obs

Client --> Http : HTTPS / JSON
Http --> App
App --> Persist
Persist --> Db : SQL
Mig ..> Db : apply

Graf --> Prom : queries
Prom ..> Http : scrape :8000/metrics
Bbx ..> Http : probe :8000/ready

note bottom of App
  Layering: API → Services → Repositories → DB
end note

@enduml
